title: Peanut Butter Chocolate Chip Cookies
ingredients: ['250g plain flour', '1 teaspoon bicarbonate of soda', '1 teaspoon salt', '225g unsalted butter', '300g caster sugar', '85g peanut butter', '1 egg', '1 teaspoon vanilla extract', '335g dark chocolate chips', "4 Reese's peanut butter cups, chopped*"]
